<subSubSection id="C30198A6FFF5FFCDFF02F88FFC5574F9" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA4CB2DFFF5FFCDFF02F88FFF257243" blockId="9.[130,775,1811,2028]" box="[132,207,1811,1837]" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">NOTES</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA4CB2DFFF5FFCDFF02F8AFFC5574F9" blockId="9.[130,775,1811,2028]" lastBlockId="9.[812,1456,216,401]" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">
In the protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BB0AEFFF5FFCDFEEEF8AFFDAB7224" authority="Lecomte" box="[360,577,1842,1868]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ebenaceae" genus="Diospyros" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="harmandii">
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFEEEF8AFFDAB7224" box="[360,577,1842,1868]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">Diospyros harmandii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8AB6DCFFF5FFCDFDC9F8AFFF5C7204" author="LECOMTE H." pageId="9" pageNumber="122" pagination="99 - 121" refId="ref13173" refString="LECOMTE H. 1928 a. - Ebenacees nouvelles de l'Indochine. Notulae Systematicae 4 (4): 99 - 121. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 6463259" type="journal article" year="1928">Lecomte (1928a: 121)</bibRefCitation>
cited 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFF76F8CEFE687204" box="[240,386,1874,1900]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">Harmand 415</emphasis>
from “ 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF5FFCDFE4EF8CEFDAA7204" box="[456,576,1874,1900]" name="Cambodia" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">Cambodge</collectingCountry>
: prov. de Kokek” as the original material. He did not cite 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BB0AEFFF5FFCDFE7BF8EFFD6372E4" authorityName=", Lecomte" authorityYear="1928" box="[509,649,1906,1932]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ebenaceae" genus="Diospyros" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="harmandii">
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFE7BF8EFFD6372E4" box="[509,649,1906,1932]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">D. harmandii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the 1930 account, neither as a species nor as a synonym. We found that the description of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BB0AEFFF5FFCDFEBAF82EFE877284" authority="Lecomte (1930: 925)" authorityName="Lecomte, Flore" authorityPageNumber="925" authorityYear="1930" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ebenaceae" genus="Diospyros" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="ehretioides" variety="harmandii">
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFEBAF82EFE2972A4" box="[316,451,1970,1996]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">D. ehretioides</emphasis>
Wall. ex G.Don var. 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFD1FF82EFCEF72A4" box="[665,773,1970,1996]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">harmandii</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8AB6DCFFF5FFCDFF02F84EFE877284" author="LECOMTE H." box="[132,365,2001,2028]" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" pagination="915 - 978" refId="ref13275" refString="LECOMTE H. 1930. - Ebenacees, in LECOMTE H. &amp; HUMBERT H. (eds), Flore generale de l'Indo-Chine. Vol. 3. Masson &amp; Co., Paris: 915 - 978. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 27563332" type="book chapter" year="1930">Lecomte (1930: 925)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
matches with 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BB0AEFFF5FFCDFD96F84EFC56759A" authority="Lecomte (1928 a: 121)" authorityName=", Lecomte" authorityPageNumber="121" authorityYear="1928" box="[528,956,216,2028]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ebenaceae" genus="Diospyros" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="harmandii">
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFD96F84EFD497283" box="[528,675,2001,2027]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">D. harmandii</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8AB6DCFFF5FFCDFD2CF84EFC56759A" author="LECOMTE H." box="[682,956,216,2028]" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" pagination="99 - 121" refId="ref13173" refString="LECOMTE H. 1928 a. - Ebenacees nouvelles de l'Indochine. Notulae Systematicae 4 (4): 99 - 121. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 6463259" type="journal article" year="1928">Lecomte (1928a: 121)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and the original material of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BB0AEFFF5FFCDFB73FF45FC76747A" authorityName="Lecomte, Flore" authorityYear="1930" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ebenaceae" genus="Diospyros" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="ehretioides" variety="harmandii">
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFB73FF45FA68759A" box="[1269,1410,216,242]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">D. ehretioides</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFCABFF64FC76747A" box="[813,924,248,274]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">harmandii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is “ 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF5FFCDFC47FF64FBD7747A" box="[961,1085,248,274]" name="Cambodia" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">Cambodge</collectingCountry>
: (
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFBC9FF64FB5C747A" box="[1103,1206,248,274]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">Harmand</emphasis>
)”. We consider 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BB0AEFFF5FFCDFAE6FF64FC927459" authorityName=", Lecomte" authorityYear="1928" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ebenaceae" genus="Diospyros" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="harmandii">
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFAE6FF64FC927459" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">D. harmandii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
a homotypic synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BB0AEFFF5FFCDFB00FE84FA457459" authorityName="Lecomte, Flore" authorityYear="1930" box="[1158,1455,279,306]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ebenaceae" genus="Diospyros" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="9" pageNumber="122" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="ehretioides" variety="harmandii">
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFB00FE84FAFA7459" box="[1158,1296,279,305]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">D. ehretioides</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFAC7FE8BFA457459" box="[1345,1455,279,305]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">harmandii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in Lecomte’s intentions. We located four sheets of 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF5FFCDFACEFEABFCBD7419" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">Harmand 415</emphasis>
at P, and here we designate the specimen P00721490 as the 
<typeStatus id="54A0758FFFF5FFCDFCD3FEEBFC5074F9" box="[853,954,375,401]" pageId="9" pageNumber="122">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
